{"tid":1022740,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"女朋友無安全感","createTime":"2019-02-15T08:35:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T20:10:58.000Z","uid":81494,"like":30,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"fa646173161c0a4087c8a837b69fe2c783267c21","tid":1022740,"uid":81494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T08:35:06.000Z","msg":"背景同女朋友拍左拖已經六年啦<br />\n由於佢屋企個老豆同姐夫都出去偷食<br />\n所以佢每日都好擔心我有機會偷食 好無安全感 覺得自己無野好 比唔上其他人<br />\n但係我已經係呢幾年同自己比較Fd既女性朋友特登保持距離<br />\n就算同同事食飯都特登帶佢出去 公開下啲關係 自己又唔會單獨同女仔出去食飯<br />\n可惜都係無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇巴打有好方法提意下點解決<br />\n或者絲打會有同感 一齊討論下？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f872fc329f0e183be35f66ce92d02ba335ccd17","tid":1022740,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":10,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T08:35:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3099a5c8e2b9298e3330959959364fb56c21589b","tid":1022740,"uid":13160,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T08:35:54.000Z","msg":"比佢電話我"},{"pid":"b94d20e1fd1a3a84a5cae2fdc91699ec0c62c73e","tid":1022740,"uid":179588,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T08:37:36.000Z","msg":"有人講過安全感呢d要靠自己<br />\n你對佢愈好，佢就愈驚冇左你，愈驚就愈冇安全感<br />\n係一個惡性循環黎<br />\n我覺得你要做既已經做晒<br />\n其仔靠佢自己"},{"pid":"10cebf74eed6464618d6808a6c0b6ba134c16422","tid":1022740,"uid":81494,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"b94d20e1fd1a3a84a5cae2fdc91699ec0c62c73e","tid":1022740,"uid":179588,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T08:37:36.000Z","msg":"有人講過安全感呢d要靠自己<br />\n你對佢愈好，佢就愈驚冇左你，愈驚就愈冇安全感<br />\n係一個惡性循環黎<br />\n我覺得你要做既已經做晒<br />\n其仔靠佢自己"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T08:40:29.000Z","msg":"點靠佢自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\"